title: Kate Winslet was nervous to meet real Joanna Hoffman for 'Steve Jobs'
text:
*Los Angeles*: Kate Winslet plays Apple co-founder's right-hand woman, Joanna Hoffman in "Steve Jobs," but the actress says she was "nervous" to meet her at first.
The Oscar-award winning star was tense before meeting Hoffman as she does not resemble her at all, reported Entertainment Weekly.*Kate Winslet. Pic/ Santa ... Â»
